title: The Keiser Report No. 127 - Mar 08 TU [sebaygo1]

The Keiser Report  No. 127
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 08 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


U.S. Gaddafies


This week Max and Stacy report from Cairo on war profiteers blaming foreign 'financial terrorists' for the economic collapse that they helped cause. They also talk about Gaddafi's billions and China's gold. 


In the second half of the show, Max talks to investigative journalist and blogger, Hisham Allam, about Egypt's revolution and what his investigations into corruption are finding in terms of the Mubarak family's loot.



The .mp3 is audio extracted from the Russia Today video. You can watch the video online at:

 that counters the monotone of mainstream corporate media.
